'''隱孢子蟲屬'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Cryptosporidium''）是[[頂複門|頂複門]]的一個[[屬|屬]]，本屬部分物種可感染包括[[人類|人類]]在內的許多[[脊椎動物|脊椎動物]]，造成[[隱孢子蟲病|隱孢子蟲病]]，症狀包括[[腹瀉|腹瀉]]與[[咳嗽|咳嗽]]等<ref name="Respiratory cryptosporidiosis - fomite transmission">{{cite journal | vauthors = Sponseller JK, Griffiths JK, Tzipori S | title = The evolution of respiratory Cryptosporidiosis: evidence for transmission by inhalation | journal = Clinical Microbiology Reviews | volume = 27 | issue = 3 | pages = 575–86 | date = July 2014 | pmid = 24982322 | pmc = 4135895 | doi = 10.1128/CMR.00115-13 }}</ref>。

==感染==
{{main|隱孢子蟲病}}
隱孢子蟲與[[瘧原蟲|瘧原蟲]]和[[弓形蟲|弓形蟲]]皆為頂複門的寄生蟲，有別於後兩者，隱孢子蟲的生活史中不需[[中間宿主|中間宿主]]<ref name=CDC_Site>{{cite web | title = Parasites - Cryptosporidium (also known as "Crypto") | url = https://www.cdc.gov/parasites/crypto/pathogen.html | publisher = Centers for Disease Control and Prevention | date = February 20, 2015 | access-date = 2020-07-10 | archive-date = 2021-05-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210506133646/https://www.cdc.gov/parasites/crypto/pathogen.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。隱孢子蟲病多為短期、急性的疾病，感染後隱孢子蟲可生存在人類的腸道長達五週，造成[[腹瀉|腹瀉]]等症狀<ref name="Respiratory cryptosporidiosis - fomite transmission"/>。在體外隱孢子蟲以[[微生物囊|卵囊]]的形式存在，對環境的抗性很高，進入人體後即可感染小腸上皮組織。造成人類隱孢子蟲病的物種大多是[[小隱孢子蟲|小隱孢子蟲]]與{{le|人隱胞子蟲|Cryptosporidium hominis}}兩種，不過[[犬隱孢子蟲|犬隱孢子蟲]]（''C. canis''）、[[貓隱孢子蟲|貓隱孢子蟲]]（''C. felis''）、[[火雞隱胞子蟲|火雞隱胞子蟲]]（''C. meleagridis''）與{{le|鼠隱孢子蟲|Cryptosporidium muris}}也可能感染人類<ref name=CDC_Site/>。[[免疫缺陷|免疫缺陷]]者被感染的症狀一般較嚴重，但免疫正常者也可能被感染<ref name=CDC_Site/>。

==基因組==
2004年，[[小隱孢子蟲|小隱孢子蟲]]的[[基因組|基因組]]被完整[[基因組定序|定序]]，發現其[[粒線體|粒線體]]中不含有[[粒線體DNA|DNA]]<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Abrahamsen MS, Templeton TJ, Enomoto S, Abrahante JE, Zhu G, Lancto CA, Deng M, Liu C, Widmer G, Tzipori S, Buck GA, Xu P, Bankier AT, Dear PH, Konfortov BA, Spriggs HF, Iyer L, Anantharaman V, Aravind L, Kapur V | title = Complete genome sequence of the apicomplexan, Cryptosporidium parvum | journal = Science | volume = 304 | issue = 5669 | pages = 441–5 | date = April 2004 | pmid = 15044751 | doi = 10.1126/science.1094786 }}</ref>。

